Can she fly a kite? → Yes, she can.
Can they write these words? → Yes, they can.
Can he sing? → No, he can't.
Can I open the window, please? → Yes, you can.
Can Doris speak French? → Yes, she can.
Can we meet our friends? → Yes, you can.
Can he ride a snowboard? → No, he can't.
Can the girls swim? → Yes, they can.
Can you help me? → Yes, I can.
Can the frog sing? → No, it can't.